The '''Endorian Grasslands''' was an area on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]] that was dominated by tall [[Grass/Legends|grass]]. It was inhabited by many [[species]], such as the [[Grass Trekker/Legends|Grass Trekkers]], and it was bordered by the [[Grass Trekkers' shrine]] and [[Gupin stronghold]].<ref name="Land of the Gupins" />

{{Loc-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The Endorian Grasslands first appeared in "[[The Land of the Gupins]],"<ref name="Land of the Gupins" /> the eighth episode of the animated television series [[Ewoks (television series)|''Ewoks'']]. The episode was written by [[Bob Carrau]] and premiered on [[October 26]], [[1985]].<ref name="Insider 27">{{InsiderCite|27|A Star Wars CELibration|A ''Star Wars'' CELibration}}</ref>

